      "type": "heading",
      "title": "Project Statement"
    },
    {
      "id": "SEC2",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Global Retail Ltd. operates a nationwide retail distribution network supplying supermarkets across South India. The company currently plans transportation manually. Due to increasing order volumes and multiple shipping locations, planners frequently select inefficient routes, trucks are underutilized and transportation costs continue to increase."
    },
